      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, what do you mean by a goblin's sense of space? i'm more interested in the physics part you mentioned—how do the frequency ratios actually affect the ear? like, can you explain the actual interference pattern or the math behind why the minor second specifically causes that tension?",
