      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't really get the goblin trap metaphor, can we just stick to the acoustics? you mentioned interference patterns—are you talking about critical bands in the cochlea? how does the proximity of those two frequencies specifically cause the physical sensation of \"roughness\"?",
      "source": "evaluator"
